INSERT INTO `tb_article` VALUES ('11', '1', null, '第二页', null, '<div>早餐鸡蛋别再煮着吃了，简单快手新做法，鸡蛋饼其实也是可以换着花样做的，就说里面添加的蔬菜就可以换成很多种，今天分享的是胡萝卜鸡蛋饼。胡萝卜本身就比较甜，和鸡蛋做成饼，既有鸡蛋的醇香又有胡萝卜的香甜，不仅孩子爱吃，全家都非常喜欢！</div>\n<p><br /><br /><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/8107105-20b83d4e9afce8a9.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<div>\n<div>鸡蛋中含有各种营养，也是每天都吃的一种食品，家家户户都离不开它，鸡蛋物美价廉，营养丰富。鸡蛋中的优质蛋白，可以保护肝脏；鸡蛋中DHA和卵磷脂可以健脑益智，小孩子每天至少一个鸡蛋哦；鸡蛋中的铁可以改善女人的面色，红润有光泽，告别黄脸婆哦！胡萝卜中含有丰富的胡萝卜素，可以保护孩子的视力！胡萝卜鸡蛋饼最大的优点就是快手简单，1分钟就能做出来，吃起来口感香软有弹性，孩子爱吃，妈妈更开心！上桌全家抢着吃，一定要学习胡萝卜鸡蛋饼的做法！</div>\n<img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/8107105-d312ed013b4490ca.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /><span style=\"color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">胡萝卜鸡蛋饼</span>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">食材：</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">面粉半碗、鸡蛋3个、盐适量、胡萝卜半根、小葱1根。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/8107105-0a28ae38f15e2b88.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">制作方法：</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">1.面粉中加入适量盐和3个鸡蛋。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/8107105-76a278e844c47b48.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">2.加入适量清水和葱花，搅拌成流动的糊状，水太少的话，饼会比较硬，影响口感，水太多也不行，饼就烙不成形</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/8107105-522fb8af7e7c7137.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">3.胡萝卜切成碎末，如果觉得切着比较麻烦，可以放入绞肉机搅拌碎。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/8107105-f35813a283f1a9a4.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">4.把胡萝卜碎放入面糊中，搅拌均匀，可以静置15分钟。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/8107105-b71d437a61ca02a1.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">5.平底锅小火加热，刷一层薄薄的食用油，舀两勺面糊，倒入锅中。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/8107105-40ba63a3b22ed480.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">6.摇晃平底锅，让面糊铺满锅底，小火煎，先不要着急翻面。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/8107105-d3e5dc4adaf5a8c8.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">7.待边缘有点起边的时候，再轻轻的翻面，边缘有点起边的时候，饼基本就熟了。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/8107105-632b0a1312137582.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">今天的分享就到这里，我是（一勺美食），希望大家能喜欢，如果大家还有什么问题？可以关注小编，给小编留言一起交流美食经验，小编每天都会为大家带来不一样的美食，不一样的做法，希望大家越吃越健康！</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/8107105-78cfd71a8d6c8b8a.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/640/format/webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">&nbsp;</p>\n</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>', null, '雪山上那个需要滚雪球撞开大门的神庙怎么过的？提示是同时并举？上面一个石球。', '8', '5', null, '1', '海拉鲁老流氓', '2020-02-20 21:11:52', '2020-02-20 21:11:52');
