INSERT INTO `tb_article` VALUES ('27', '2', null, '小学生教育父母：我都会用古诗说服人，你们只会嗷嗷喊', null, '<p>近日，</p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>一段&ldquo;小女孩教育家长&rdquo;的视频火了&nbsp;</p>\n<p>视频中</p>\n<p>小女孩因被家长批评不服气</p>\n<p>转过头来开始教育家长</p>\n<p>如何正确对待孩子</p>\n<p>她还一脸严肃地指出</p>\n<p>家长应该用文明的语言</p>\n<p>批评人也要用古诗、名句</p>\n<p>&ldquo;文化人要用古诗批评人，</p>\n<p>你那样啊啊啊啊喊，</p>\n<p>谁想听你们的啊？&rdquo;</p>\n<p>一番妙语连珠逗笑网友。</p>\n<p>视频里，</p>\n<p>小女孩被爸爸批评以后，</p>\n<p>沮丧地坐在凳子上，</p>\n<p>可下一秒钟对着沙发上的爸爸</p>\n<p>就是一通&ldquo;语重心长&rdquo;地说教。</p>\n</div>\n<img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/14621973-3984ccd75b31a870.jpg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/450/format/webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"547\" /><br />\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">妙语连珠</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">你看人家动画片里面那些，他们是怎样对孩子的？不骂孩子~不打孩子~只是批评她，让她改正。</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/14621973-370c1460fa318476.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/328/format/webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"328\" height=\"203\" /></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\">而你们就那样，啊啊啊啊喊，谁想听你们的啊？</span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 600;\"><img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/14621973-7677daf4b1c8372d.gif?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/344/format/webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"344\" height=\"292\" /></span></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>说完之后小女孩没有停下来，</p>\n<p>而像个大人一样，</p>\n<p>继续讲道理。</p>\n<p>你看很多父母是不是（有）小孩子跟我一样，很调皮也很聪明？</p>\n<p>她们父母就像你一样打她骂她。</p>\n<p>她们是不是越来越笨？被骂笨了。还打？打个半死去哦！</p>\n</div>\n<img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/14621973-74b240732a8c093d.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/584/format/webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"584\" height=\"523\" /></div>\n<div><img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/14621973-61039f697bcfc136.gif?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/344/format/webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"344\" height=\"292\" /></div>\n<div>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">小女孩进一步指出父母的问题</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">你们都读了大学了</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">还不会用好的句子骂人</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">我连小学都还没有读完</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; word-break: break-word; color: #404040; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Segoe UI\', \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #ffffff;\">自己都不反省</p>\n<div class=\"image-package\"